{"tid":1545491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[難d fc但都心知肚明]有黑社會混入前線當中","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:24:42.000Z","uid":149212,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"25558e581fc46e33c79ccba7718c15efb14aa57f","tid":1545491,"uid":149212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"朋友屋企人係一個幫派入面幾話得事（呢個已fc），親口承認自612起有勢力出左一大筆錢要混入前線搞破壞，全港所有幫派都有參與，目的係要抹黑義士<br />\n掘磚 拆鐵馬 鋸燈柱 鑽水馬 汽油彈 等等聲稱係佢地做，理由係手法純熟，裝備高級齊全<br />\n朋友屋企人睇示威片段會屌鳩義士，但當朋友寸佢話「扮咩，你屌緊個班咪係你自己d人」佢當堂無再出聲<br />\n當然，前線有鬼大家一直都知，事情發展咁多個月，民意歸晒邊都唔怕抹黑，前線手足做咩核彈都唔割，對方咁樣出錢反而令勇武手足贏得掌聲，真係出事又可以賴係鬼做，何樂而不為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eb7fc2e709a71fa57827f3669c79a82b49886d","tid":1545491,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:35:35.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc61036e16cb3632b40d272c63b60b441fb8803a","tid":1545491,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:36:49.000Z","msg":"外星人用變型術混入左示威者(已fc)<br />\n大家小心被捉走"},{"pid":"b6a3441647efd344d80692b87ba93625b134927f","tid":1545491,"uid":297835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"又朋友<br />\n又已fc<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}